<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.8.9">
<l>poṅkēṟu nīḷcōtip poṉṉāḻi taṉṉōṭum</l>
<l>caṅkēṟu kōlat taṭakkaip perumāṉai</l>
<l>koṅkēṟu cōlaik kuṭantaik kiṭantāṉai</l>
<l>naṅkōṉai nāṭi naṟaiyūril kaṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having searched for our king, the great lord</l>
<l>In whose fine, broad hands the conch rises</l>
<l>Along with the golden discus with a great radiance that rises, radiating,</l>
<l>The one who sleeps in Kuṭantai with forests where fragrance rises,</l>
<l rend="indent">I saw [him] in Naṟaiyūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
